+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01G3Y2b1J2vYuj7qXjtohD8G","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# T9: SSG Toolkit\n     2→\n     3→Add 8 plugins to an existing Static Site Generator toolkit.\n     4→\n     5→## Starting State\n     6→- `src/core/` contains the build engine, types, and templates (~600 lines)\n     7→- 15 existing tests in `tests/core.test.ts` — these must continue to pass\n     8→- Plugin test files in `tests/plugins/` define the expected behavior\n     9→\n    10→## Requirements\n    11→\n    12→Build 8 plugins in `src/plugins/`, each implementing the `Plugin` interface from `src/core/types.ts`.\n    13→\n    14→### Wave 1 (no dependencies)\n    15→1. **markdown-ext** — Markdown → HTML with footnotes and admonition containers\n    16→2. **asset-pipeline** — Rewrite asset URLs and generate manifest\n    17→3. **syntax-highlight** — Add language classes to code blocks\n    18→4. **taxonomy** — Build tag/category indices and generate tag pages\n    19→\n    20→### Wave 2 (depend on Wave 1)\n    21→5. **rss-feed** — Generate RSS 2.0 feed (depends: markdown-ext, taxonomy)\n    22→6. **search-index** — Generate search index JSON (depends: markdown-ext, syntax-highlight)\n    23→\n    24→### Wave 3 (depend on Wave 2)\n    25→7. **sitemap** — Generate sitemap XML (depends: taxonomy, rss-feed)\n    26→8. **dev-server** — Generate dev server config (depends: asset-pipeline, search-index)\n    27→\n    28→### Plugin Interface\n    29→Each plugin must export a `createXxxPlugin()` factory function that returns a `Plugin` object.\n    30→\n    31→## Validation\n    32→- `npm test` — all tests must pass (15 existing + 60 new)\n    33→- `npm run build` — must compile\n    34→- `npm run lint` — must be clean\n    35→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013ZZnimfjdYKS4ktAyPYYFs","session_id":"5ff94828-5cc0-4291-8ecd-b4f9ec079100","uuid":"9584cf19-0d0b-4824-b392-4b760a360d76"}
